Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the rhythm of the wind, deductions become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figuring out the alibi trick!
Comment: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Comment: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that one truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Comment: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't, Ruri-ppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:35.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you forgotten? About my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ujou Ruri (37)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, he was pretty famous in the neighborhood for his hatred of smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! As a result, his outlook toward smoking transferred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then, that makes you the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.64,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Nobuharu (31)\NActor - Nagumo Akira's Son
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, my mother was the one in my house who disliked smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:53.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira (60)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She even got my father, who had been a heavy smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,To quit smoking as soon as I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what do you do for scenes in dramas where you have to smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In those cases, I just hold a cigarette in my lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep—when we're forced to by the director or the producer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, no matter how much time goes by, you'll always be a second-rate actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.33,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Namihara Kasumi (26)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for a certain someone who sells herself as being a refreshing actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be good for her healthy image.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of me, who can converse with him so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as the murdered Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that those two are lovers off-screen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the lover that this person is secretly meeting with...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do know who the culprit is yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bother the police, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding your courtship of her - I'm asking what you're intending to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, about Ruri-ppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not courting her - we're just childhood friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is just that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you do anything unsightly, I won't forgive you even if you are a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like I've had this feeling before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This toolbox was left unattended in this room along with the golf gloves and the coat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I was thinking that, besides a box-cutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There might there be something else in here that could be used for cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to play detective, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just know the police already searched that toolbox top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even this tape measure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spiking a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, spiking is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's using sticky tape to mark a place on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like where to put set furniture and where the actors should stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the filming will probably be canceled, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,: Just in case, I guess I'll remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something strange about this sticky tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bulging a little, and something's stuck at the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cotton?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, now I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the weapon was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason why it hasn't been found!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the coat and the gloves having been left here in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a simple task to commit the crime in this room 7 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left is who did it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The behavior of Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who saw snow from that window and suddenly compelled everyone to go outside to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! It's Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That brat, loitering around the scene of the crime again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Inspector Yokomizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went outside a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you all smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to take another look at the evidence, so can I borrow some gloves from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... This is the wallet, these are the cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coat, the gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's out of lighter fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've solved the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to put Uncle to sleep with this tranquilizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tranquilizer dart isn't coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I used it up during the camera rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't produce "Sleeping Kogorou" like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's like this, I'll have to give Uncle a lot of hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed a lot of things, will you hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it'll help you solve the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solved the ease?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nowhere really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just walking around this house looking for keys to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you solved it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mystery of the vanished weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, what I found weren't keys, but this brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then well continue the search for the weapon, so if you there's anything you notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll let you know right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only I could use the tranquilizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His expression changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's figured out the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe, I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! That person's not the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have to hit Uncle on the head with something to make him lose consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something to kick... Something to kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's locked! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's locked, I can't go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the matter, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Locking the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you want to seduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't hear the conversation inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most I can do is throw this transmitter through the gap under the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:09:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think that I'm the culprit who murdered Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And want to persuade me to turn myself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to recommend confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, Uncle's in the wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop him soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to recommend confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, Uncle's in the wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop him soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one I want to confess isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one you're covering for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I have to protect Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right before you noticed the falling snow outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the staff in the room next to the window opened the door and came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should have been reflected in the glass embedded in that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The figure of Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who had just come out of the next room where Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The figure of the murderer who was about to leave the room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon noticing the staff, was surprised and shut himself back into the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging by that behavior, you suspected that he may have perpetrated some sort of act...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by telling everyone to go outside to see the snow, you made sure no one went near that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed that just a little while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Conan was by the door of the crime scene, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found him before turning the corner of the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was reflected in the glass of that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"As expected of the great detective," is what I'd like to say at this point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon hasn't been found yet, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blade that sliced through the napping Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than the imaginary story that says I witnessed the murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you first solve the mystery of the disappearing 10-centimeter long blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been so fixated on searching for a 10-centimeter long blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likely because no one considered that it could have been transformed into a 2-centimeter long lump of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the box-cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After murdering Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the culprit broke the blade into small pieces, and hid the collected ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the lighter that Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You got it, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if bloody box-cutter blades are found inside that lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't necessarily mean that the weapon has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blade had to be 10 centimeters long in order to be able to cut so deeply into the neck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the blades aren't properly inserted into the box-cutter's grip, it wouldn't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as for that grip, shouldn't blood have spurted onto it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, they should have found a box-cutter grip that reacted to the luminol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, come on Uncle! Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First you'd have to find the grip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right... Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:47.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Translator's Note: "Gamu teepu" means sticky tape. Conan is quoting the word "Gum," which in Japanese generally calls for the particle "te" after the quoted word or phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Gum"-te! Do you have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gum... Te?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as anti-drowsiness gum, I think I brought it since Dad asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(gamu teepu)\NIt's sticky tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:14:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the box-cutter were wrapped with sticky tape from the grip to the end of the blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be possible to avoid having blood spurt onto the grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the crime, he peeled off the blood-covered tape, and probably stuck it to the floor on the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, on that floor, there are sticky-tape markings everywhere which made it difficult to take note of!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why does that mean it had to be Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that kind of trick, I could have done it because I was the first to find the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the snow as a distraction, I could use the opportunity to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's stupid! That you would kill anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, how stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, it looks like the gum is inside the rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you put on a brassiere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, I've never used one, so I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here! Boys don't need to know that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This crime is impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you hide the box-cutter blades in this lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, inside the cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything under the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s deduction must be wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your saying that Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the culprit must be wrong too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This type of lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the kind where you add the lighter fluid onto the cotton that's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, without first removing the bottom, and then taking out the cotton that's inside to make space...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blades of the box-cutter cannot be hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw that the lighter wouldn't light, I realized that meant the cotton had been removed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for you, a person who hates smoking and has never used a lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd never think that something could be hidden there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we consider that this person would not only think of that, but would also be someone you'd want to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could only be the ex-heavy smoker Nagumo Akira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I said it earlier, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I want to protect Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I meet him every now and then for work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We aren't that dose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's your...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lover, lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Real father, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a single item used during the crime that was prepared in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, it was a haphazard crime that was thought up on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cotton, heavy with the scent of the lighter fluid, was probably covered up by the sticky tape on the set, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would probably be found as soon as someone looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:17:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After committing the crime, in a situation where anyone could have come in at any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking the cotton out from the lighter and putting the box-cutter blades inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be impossible to do while still wearing gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a certainty that fingerprints would have been left somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, before the evidence becomes known, have your father turn himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira is my real father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was conceived during the time that he and my mother were both members of a failing theater troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though my mother was pregnant, she didn't realize it until after she had broken up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And had started dating the man that you, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, knew as my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was something I never would have imagined in my wildest dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I co-starred with him, and he said that I looked just like his own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked my mother for the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had called asking to meet with me, so I went to complain to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, "It's too late for you to play the role of my father."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right in front of me, he broke down and cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I met with him every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, a father is always a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His killing of Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was known that he was my real father, it would be a big mess for my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a big favor to a childhood friend, can you keep his crime to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that sort of deal, especially since it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I wouldn't want my childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be bound by such a heartbreaking, sorrowful lie for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That part of you hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called you over himself and told you the truth about our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, at that time, he didn't say anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how did you know we were father and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I realized it from Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that of a man facing down a rival who was courting his lover, but instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same feeling I had picked up on when I went to meet Eri's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a father's worry for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, as expected, it's Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm no match for her, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't Eri, it was her stubborn father that I was reminded of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During middle school, the reason why I studied extra hard to the point where I had to wear glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was because I wanted to catch a certain someone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was certain that you liked smart girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result of her persuasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} turned himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this real-life mystery drama came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? You met Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was surely even more beautiful than she seems on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That she was the actress Ujou Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, unlike that person, I went to the class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I heard all kinds of things from Ujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like how Mom and Dad had a big quarrel over soy sauce and Worcestershire sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was because he always puts Worcestershire sauce on sunny-side-up fried eggs when he's alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he's with me, he gets embarrassed and forces himself to use soy sauce - it really bugged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, Dad does always put Worcestershire sauce on his sunny-side-up fried eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just that dense of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing from so long ago, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, these gloves - which do you think are better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I think I'd go with the black ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think these gray ones seem better.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because gray is written "mouse color"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A color with an animal's name in it, doesn't it seem like it'd be warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the gray tablecloth seemed warmer than the black coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did I say something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You strange child...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a strange old man...
